link: Max Alekseyev, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..100
C. J. Hillar, D. Rhea. Automorphisms of finite Abelian groups. American Mathematical Monthly 114:10 (2007), 917-923. Preprint arXiv:math/0605185 [math.GR]

Index entries for sequences related to enumerating groups.
formula: a(n) = Sum n!/|Aut(G)|, where the sum is taken over the different products G of cyclic groups with |G|=n. Formula for |Aut(G)| is given by Hillar and Rhea (2007).
